<item>
            <title>[SOLR-15648] ManagedSchema#GetZkSchemaVersionCallable can get into a loop that wants to go on for 10 minutes before it cuts off.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-15648</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s a balancing act improving tests at all - you go too far and you start having to deal with all the underlying issues. Doing my best to avoid that, but a test not even related to managed schema wanting to retry fruitlessly to contact a server that is never going to give in for 10 minutes is a little much.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
